videos.description: Steph Curry uses a saucy crossover to lose Robert Covington, then attacks and finishes with a nice layup in the paint.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Curry crosses up Covington for Warriors bucket) 2021/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Curry crosses up Covington for Warriors bucket

videos.description: Steph Curry recognizes Enes Kanter is guarding him and goes up using a smooth reverse layup to avoid the block and get the bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Curry uses sweet reverse against Kanter) 2021/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Curry uses sweet reverse against Kanter

videos.description: Steph Curry quickly heats up as he scores 21 points in the first quarter against the Trail Blazers.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Curry put up 21 points in the first quarter vs. Blazers) 2021/01/03 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Curry put up 21 points in the first quarter vs. Blazers

videos.description: Draymond Green passes to Kelly Oubre, who rises up to stuff down an authoritative one-haded dunk on the fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Oubre throws down fast-break jam) 2021/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oubre throws down fast-break jam

videos.description: To end the third quarter, Damian Lillard gets the pass in the corner with 1.7 seconds left and hits a tough jumpshot as he fades away out of bounds to beat the buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lillard hits tough fadeaway jumper to end the 3rd quarter) 2021/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lillard hits tough fadeaway jumper to end the 3rd quarter

videos.description: Steph Curry knocks down an unreal, off-balance 3-pointer to give him 62 points on the night.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Curry's off-balance 3-pointer gives him 62 points) 2021/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Curry's off-balance 3-pointer gives him 62 points

videos.description: Despite Damian Lillard's 32 points, the Trail Blazers couldn't stop the Warriors offense as Steph Curry puts up 62 points to lead Golden State to a 137-122 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Warriors take down Portland 137-122 in hard-fought win) 2021/01/03 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Warriors take down Portland 137-122 in hard-fought win

videos.description: Steph Curry contends that he has to take the good with the bad when it comes to dealing with his critics.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Curry on critics: 'I like being talked about') 2021/01/03

videos.headline: Curry on critics: 'I like being talked about'
